        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName><hi rend="print">Down.</hi> | Beckenham | <hi rend="print">Kent. S.E.</hi></placeName>
                    <date>Jan 15<hi rend="superscript">th</hi>.</date>
                    <salute>My dear Sir</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>I am very sorry to hear of your accident, which seems to have been of a serious nature. I received the fruit all safely, and guessed that the specimens were sent by you. I was surprised at the vine with red leaves, and admired much the beans of the Phaseolus<ref target="#foot.f2"/></p>
<p>Your new residence sounds very delightful, and I hope that it will suit you in every respect.</p>
<p>Pray believe me My dear Sir | yours very faithfully | Ch. Darwin</p> 
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="tnotes">
                <note xml:id="tnote.n1">3.1 My … Darwin] <hi rend="italic">in CD’s hand</hi> </note>
            </div>

            
            
            
            
        </div>

        

        

